              Quick Install
            </h3>
            <div
              class="code-block p-4 rounded-md font-mono text-sm text-gray-300 overflow-x-auto relative"
            >
              <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/DualHorizon/malbox.git
  cd malbox
  
  # Configure
  cp configuration/malbox.example.toml configuration/malbox.toml
  $EDITOR configuration/malbox.toml
  
  # Build and Run
  cargo build --release
  cargo run --release</code></pre>
