            Malbox also provides Docker images for quick deployment without
            dealing with dependencies.
          </p>
          <div
            class="code-block p-4 rounded-md font-mono text-sm text-gray-300 overflow-x-auto relative mb-8"
          >
            <pre><code># Pull official image
  docker pull malbox/malbox:latest
  
  # Start with docker-compose
  wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DualHorizon/malbox/main/docker-compose.yml
  docker-compose up -d</code></pre>
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-500/5 animate-shimmer opacity-30 pointer-events-none"
